Iya, tentu.</i></font>

450
00:30:48,889 --> 00:30:50,789
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Mengapa?</i></font>

451
00:30:50,789 --> 00:30:52,359
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan menyingkirkannya dengan tenang.</i></font>

452
00:30:52,359 --> 00:30:55,599
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kehidupannya pasti sangat melelahkan.</i></font>

453
00:30:55,599 --> 00:30:57,569
